title: Senior Developer
description: MYOB is a business platform. Our purpose is to help more businesses in Australia and New Zealand start, survive and succeed. Our team is continually growing, inventing, and disrupting conventions. To make all this happen, we are dedicated in creating an exceptional flexible employee experience for all team members and offer a culture where you can be yourself. We don’t want you to simply ‘fit’ into our already established culture, we want you to come and add to it, and make it even better!

title: Senior Developer
description: We are currently looking for a driven Quality Analyst with a minimum of 3 years experience to help us expand and maintain our Cloud ERP hosting solution. In this role analysts can use their exceptional analytical and communication skills to collaborate and deliver value. You will be involved in the planning, managing of risk and deliver of features, shaping our quality strategy and maintaining & enhancing our automation test suite.
